          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The scattering chamber was filled with helium gas to a",
                "pressure of 40 cm of mercury."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "CSICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Elastic scattered deuterons and recoil alpha",
                "particles were detected with CsI(Tl). When detecting",
                "deuterons, it was arranged that the thickness of the",
                "crystal just exceeded the range of the deuterons",
                "entering it.",
                "The balance of the differential cross section was",
                "measured by observing recoil alpha-particles at",
                "scattering angles smaller than 42 degr. In this case",
                "the use of a CsI(Tl) crystal, 0.3 mm thick, gave alpha",
                "pulses separated from those due to other particles."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Measurements at different angles were normalized to",
                "each other by means of a monitor counter, which",
                "observed deuterons scattered by the target gas at a",
                "fixed  angle of 20 degr.",
                "A 10 mg/cm2 thick polyethylene target placed in the",
                "incident beam and observed with a second monitor",
                "counter at an angle of 90 degr. to determine certain",
                "background components such as multiple slit edge",
                "scattering."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
